Mutual Fund Centre

HSBC Mutual Fund product details
      HSBC Mutual Fund offers a wide range of products from equity schemes to debt schemes. An individual investor can select from amongst our equity funds or our debt funds based on his financial objectives, risk appetite as well as his life stage. This section provides HSBC Mutual Fund product details at a glance.

NAV of HSBC Mutual Fund schemes
      Daily fund prices of all schemes of HSBC Mutual Fund (except HSBC Small Cap Fund) at your fingertips. In this section, you can check out the NAV of the equity or debt schemes in which you have invested your money or you can use this section to look at the current NAVs of HSBC Mutual Fund schemes that you may want to invest in.

Dividends
      Dividends are declared in HSBC Mutual Fund schemes from time to time subject to availability of distributable surplus in the scheme. This section details out the dividends declared in our equity as well as debt schemes. It contains historical information on dividends declared and hence you can check out the past history of dividends declared in a specific mutual fund scheme as well.

Invest online
      You can now invest online in HSBC Mutual Fund schemes through our online channel partners. Click here to invest online at your convenience.

















